# Character Abilities
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Craft Wondrous Item|TYPE:ItemCreation.Wizard|DESC:You can create any wondrous item whose prerequisites you meet.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Silent Spell|TYPE:Metamagic.Wizard|DESC:A silent spell can be cast with no verbal components. Spells without verbal components are not affected. A silent spell uses up a spell slot one level higher than the spell's actual level.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Brew Potion|TYPE:ItemCreation.Wizard|DESC:You can create a potion of any 3rd-level or lower spell that you know and that targets one or more creatures.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Magical Aptitude|TYPE:General|DESC:You get a +2 bonus on all Spellcraft checks and Use Magic Device checks.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Dodge|TYPE:General.Fighter.ModifyAC|DESC:During your action, you designate an opponent and receive a +1 dodge bonus to Armor Class against attacks from that opponent.
ABILITY:FEAT|TYPE:NORMAL|CATEGORY:FEAT|KEY:Spell Penetration|TYPE:General.EpicWizard.CosmicDescryer|DESC:You get a +2 bonus on caster level checks (1d20 + caster level) made to overcome a creature's spell resistance.
